"but it is envisioned that the RRID metadata schema, which was described in "
"detail previously,\\ [#bandrowski2012]_ and extended by UsedIT, will be "
"interoperable with instrument instance (PIDINST) PIDs. This interoperability"
" should enable any project to quickly download data about the model to "
"consistently fill mapped fields."
