#: ../../white-paper/publishing.rst:4
msgid ""
"To create new PIDs and assign them to instruments, institutional instrument "
"providers will submit a metadata record following the PIDINST metadata "
"schema and a URL for the landing page of the instrument to a PID provider "
"that is compliant with RDA PIDINST recommendations. Thus, it is necessary to"
" become a member of the PID provider to publish PIDs directly, or work with "
"one of their current members or registration repositories to publish PIDs on"
" behalf of the institutional instrument provider. Current PID providers "
"known to be suitable with RDA PIDINST are `ePIC`_ and `DataCite`_, but "
"PIDINST is not limited to these providers; others may implement the schema, "
"too."
